Citic Securities Said to Sell $1.7 Billion Shares, Less Than Amount Sought

-- B y   F o x   H u
-- 
2011-09-28T03:06:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/citic-securities-said-to-sell-1-7-billion-shares-less-than-amount-sought.html
Citic Securities Co. raised about
HK$13 billion ($1.7 billion) in a Hong Kong share sale, two
people with knowledge of the matter said. The company agreed to
sell the shares at HK$13.30 each, the people said, asking not to
be identified because the details are not public yet.  To contact the reporter on this story:
